'''Xashiish''' waa mid ka mid ah maandooriyada mamnuuca ka ah soomaaliya,  waxaana lagu xusay qaanuunka ciqaabta ee [[Soomaaliya]] [[1971]].<ref name="GanzglassSomalia1971">{{cite book|author1=Martin R. Ganzglass|author2=Somalia|title=The Penal code of the Somali Democratic Republic: with cases, commentary, and examples|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=MOs-AQAAIAAJ|year=1971|publisher=Rutgers University Press|isbn=978-0-8135-0667-8}}</ref>  Warbixinadii 1970 iyo [[1971]] waxay xuseysaa inay tahay mid ka mid ah maandooriyeyaasha yar ee lagu arkay soomaaliya, ee aan ahayn caleenta [[Jaad|qaadka]].<ref>{{cite book|title=New Era|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=djMOAQAAMAAJ|year=1970|publisher=Ministry of Information and National Guidance|page=18}}</ref><ref name="GanzglassSomalia1971"/>{{rp|381}} sidoo kale 2015 waxaa deegaanka [[Bacaadle]] oo dhinaca Koofureed kaga yaal magaalada Jowhar lagu arkay Xashiishka maandooriyaha oo laga soo guray beer halkaas ka baxdo, ninkii beertaas lahaa neh lagu xukumay 4 sano oo xarig ah.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.caasimada.net/arag-sawirro-beeraha-xashiishka-ee-somalia/|title=beeraha xashiishka ee soomaaliya}}</ref>


== Dagaalkii Sokeeye ee Soomaaliya ==
